AMERICAN media personality Paris Hilton said she loves our very own DJ Black Coffee. The  well-known businesswoman, socialite, model, singer, actress, fashion designer and DJ. Hilton is a great-granddaughter of Conrad Hilton, the founder of Hilton Hotels was speaking to TV host and Zimbabwean born celebrity reporter Makho Ndlovu during an interview for #peoplenow.  In the video, you can hear Makho saying: " Hi gorgeous people, I am here with the gorgeous Paris Hilton. We were talking about Black Coffee, "You were saying? Paris: " I love him his the best. We love him so much' DJ BlacK Coffee responded by saying: "She's the best" on Twitter   